{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/kw-06292023123331.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-06-29T15:55:00-04:00", "modified time": "2023-06-29T16:14:26-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "\u4e2d\u56fd&quot;\u516c\u6c11\u6cd5\u5ead&quot;\u6210\u7acb\u3000\u53d1\u8d77\u4eba\uff1a\u63a8\u52a8\u793e\u4f1a\u548c\u5e73\u8f6c\u578b", "description": "\u8fd1\u65e5\uff0c\u7531\u4e2d\u56fd\u6d77\u5916\u6d41\u4ea1\u5f8b\u5e08\u7fa4\u4f53\u53d1\u8d77\u7684\"\u516c\u6c11\u6cd5\u5ead\"\u5ba3\u5e03\u6210\u7acb\u3002\u672c\u53f0\u9488\u5bf9\u6cd5\u5ead\u6210\u7acb\u7684\u76ee\u7684\u548c\u9996\u6279\u5173\u6ce8\u54ea\u4e9b\u6848\u4ef6\u7b49\u4fe1\u606f\uff0c\u91c7\u8bbf\u4e86\u90e8\u5206\u53d1\u8d77\u4eba\u58eb\u3002", "videos": [], "audios": ["https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/kw-06292023123331.html/@@stream"], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/kw-06292023123331.html/@@images/22d7f17e-4961-454e-a13b-6653e3833b4c.jpeg\"/>\n\u4e0e\u65e5\u524d\u6210\u7acb\u7684\"\u516c\u6c11\u6cd5\u5ead\"\u76f8\u5bf9\u7684\u4e2d\u56fd\u5b98\u65b9\"\u4eba\u6c11\u6cd5\u9662\"\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/kw-06292023123331.html/@@images/image\">\n <img src=\"https://www.rfa.org//++plone++rfa-resources/img/icon-zoom.png\"/>\n</a>\n\u6cd5\u65b0\u793e\u8d44\u6599\u56fe\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n var audio_title = {\"audio_name\": \"\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\\"\\u516c\\u6c11\\u6cd5\\u5ead\\\"\\u6210\\u7acb\\u3000\\u53d1\\u8d77\\u4eba\\uff1a\\u63a8\\u52a8\\u793e\\u4f1a\\u548c\\u5e73\\u8f6c\\u578b\"};\n</script>\n<script>\n eventer = function(id){\n            var data = {\n                    \"tealium_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"on_page_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"audio_name\": audio_title['audio_name'],\n           